164
00:10:32,962 --> 00:10:33,962
Mine!

165
00:10:33,962 --> 00:10:34,962
No, leave it!

166
00:10:34,962 --> 00:10:35,962
It's mine!

167
00:10:35,962 --> 00:10:37,666
The sausages are for me!

168
